00:10:18,957 --> 00:10:19,867
好吧，
Do that.

175
00:10:21,487 --> 00:10:22,667
不过你要拿她怎么办？
So what will you do with her?

176
00:10:29,229 --> 00:10:30,439
我不要她呆在这里
 I don't want her.  Say again?

177
00:10:30,449 --> 00:10:31,519
再说一次？
I don't want her. It's nice of you to think of it--

178
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:33,790
我不要她，你们想得倒是好…

179
00:10:33,890 --> 00:10:35,730
你不是要个奴隶吗？一直都想要的
But you want a slave. You keep asking for one,

180
00:10:35,730 --> 00:10:38,161
这就给你带了一个来，波罗没法安置她，我们又不用花钱
and here she is. Pullo can't keep her, and it costs us nothing.

181
00:10:38,161 --> 00:10:39,591
我就不能要一个你的高卢奴隶？
Can't I have one of your Gaulish slaves?

182
00:10:39,591 --> 00:10:41,792
我跟你说过，我的高卢奴隶还没驯化呢
I've told you, my Gauls are unseasoned.

183
00:10:41,862 --> 00:10:43,582
擦完地板就会把你的喉咙给割了
Cut your throat as soon as sweep your floor.

184
00:10:43,582 --> 00:10:45,223
这个受过训练，又干净又听话
This one's trained up nice and docile.

185
00:10:45,233 --> 00:10:46,313
她有什么不好的？
What is wrong with her?

186
00:10:49,664 --> 00:10:51,484
她的眼神很奇怪
 She has strange eyes.  You drive me insane!

187
00:10:51,534 --> 00:10:53,014
你快让我疯了

188
00:10:54,205 --> 00:10:55,755
女孩儿留下来
The girl stays.

189
00:11:04,577 --> 00:11:07,738
冷静点，宝贝，冷静点
Keep calm, sweetie. Keep calm.

190
00:11:07,808 --> 00:11:09,218
我怎么能冷静，波罗
How can I be calm when Pullo's put that little witch to spy on me?

191
00:11:09,228 --> 00:11:10,858
把那个小贱人留下来监视我

192
00:11:10,978 --> 00:11:13,009
他知道了，莉莎，他知道了
He knows, Rissa, he knows.

193
00:11:13,109 --> 00:11:14,709
就他那样的傻大个儿？
Big simple brute like that?

194
00:11:14,709 --> 00:11:16,610
就算他怀疑什么事情
If he even suspected anything,

195
00:11:16,610 --> 00:11:19,180
他肯定会马上告诉乌瑞纳斯的，不是吗？
he'd go straight to vorenus and tell him, wouldn't he?

196
00:11:19,180 --> 00:11:20,911
你真的这么想？
 Course he would.  You really think?

197
00:11:21,211 --> 00:11:23,711
 他什么都不知道  真的？
 He doesn't know nothing.  Really?

198
00:11:23,711 --> 00:11:27,282
当然了。他看到伊万达在你的房子里
Sure of it. So he saw Evander round your house.

199
00:11:27,282 --> 00:11:29,383
那又怎么样？他是你的家人，当然可以进来
So what? He's family. He's allowed.

200
00:11:29,683 --> 00:11:32,453
 那倒是  你不用担心的
 That's true.  You're getting worried over nothing.

201
00:11:34,414 --> 00:11:36,354
上帝，希望如此吧
Gods, let it be so.

202
00:11:36,554 --> 00:11:38,835
那个可怜虫把你要的都给你了
Poor sad wretch gives everything you asked for.

203
00:11:39,485 --> 00:11:42,085
元老院认可你的地位
The Senate will ratify your status,

204
00:11:42,085 --> 00:11:44,616
你得到胜利，成为执政官
you get your triumph, stand for consul,

205
00:11:44,616 --> 00:11:47,387
而庞贝就撤退到西班牙
and Pompey shall withdraw to Spain.

206
00:11:47,387 --> 00:11:49,827
要是我们要求的话估计他还会答应亲波斯卡的小鸡鸡呢
He'll suck Posca's cock if asked nicely.

207
00:11:49,927 --> 00:11:51,337
这也太慷慨了吧
Too generous by far. I never thought for an instant

208
00:11:51,337 --> 00:11:54,058
我从未想过要接受这样的条款
 Pompey would accept such terms.  You think it's a stratagem?

209
00:11:54,058 --> 00:11:55,488
你认为这是他的诡计？
I doubt it.

210
00:11:55,658 --> 00:11:56,889
