他和他的军队都已经被困了
He and what few forces he has are trapped.

212
00:12:00,430 --> 00:12:02,970
他已经弱下来了，而且每天都在败落
He's weak and growing weaker every day.

213
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:05,361
我们随时都可以让他完蛋
We might crush him at will.

214
00:12:05,901 --> 00:12:08,251
不过既然他答应了休战
But now that he has offered truce,

215
00:12:08,501 --> 00:12:12,182
