Calm yourself, Mother, please. You've become unbalanced.

311
00:18:36,989 --> 00:18:39,040
冷静点，妈妈，你都快神经错乱了

312
00:18:39,140 --> 00:18:40,810
为什么要管谁和他上床呢？
Why care so much who he beds? It is trivium.

313
00:18:40,810 --> 00:18:41,640
这都是小事
How you take after your father- simple as milk.

314
00:18:42,150 --> 00:18:44,481
你怎么跟你爸爸一样，单纯

315
00:18:44,481 --> 00:18:46,101
要不是他在床上
If he were not mewling in bed with that witch he would be chasing down Pompey.

316
00:18:46,111 --> 00:18:48,222
跟那个婊子缠绵，他早就追杀庞贝去了

317
00:18:48,252 --> 00:18:49,822
这可不是小事，
It is not trivium. The Republic is at stake.

318
00:18:49,922 --> 00:18:51,673
共和国现在很危险
Since when do you care about the Republic?

319
00:18:51,723 --> 00:18:54,003
你什么时候开始关心共和国的？

320
00:18:54,053 --> 00:18:56,074
我一直关心共和国
I care deeply about the Republic.

321
00:18:56,084 --> 00:18:57,024
很不明智
It would be very unwise to cause trouble about this.

322
00:18:57,034 --> 00:18:58,514
为了这个生事

323
