当然了，
Of course. I wouldn't lower myself.

324
00:19:00,385 --> 00:19:02,145
我不会自降身价的

325
00:19:04,485 --> 00:19:08,156
这对肮脏的狗男女自然会被曝光的
Such sordid couplings have a way of turning out badly anyhow...

326
00:19:08,186 --> 00:19:10,787
不需要任何人干什么
by no one's special doing.

327
00:19:11,727 --> 00:19:13,187
家庭教师来了
 Tutor has arrived.  Oh good.

328
00:19:13,357 --> 00:19:14,778
哦，好

329
00:19:16,358 --> 00:19:19,719
你的老师来了，在后院等呢
Your tutor has arrived and waits in the rear yard.

330
00:19:19,719 --> 00:19:21,429
老师？什么老师？
Tutor? What tutor?

331
00:19:21,429 --> 00:19:24,090
你早就该学学男人的技艺了
It's high time you learned the masculine arts.

332
00:19:24,390 --> 00:19:25,150
如何格斗
How to fight and copulate and skin animals and so forth.

333
00:19:25,350 --> 00:19:27,231
如何交媾，还有如何给动物剥皮

334
00:19:27,331 --> 00:19:27,971
一切类似的东西
There's plenty of time yet for all that.

335
00:19:27,991 --> 00:19:29,541
要学那些还有很长时间呢

336
00:19:29,631 --> 00:19:33,092
