I cannot agree. The Greek philosophers have much to teach us.

340
00:19:38,733 --> 00:19:40,614
希腊的智者教会了我们很多东西

341
00:19:41,064 --> 00:19:42,784
那么，这就是一个希腊智者
Well, here's a Greek philosopher for you.

342
00:19:45,275 --> 00:19:47,785
我把你的那个士兵叫来了
I've engaged that soldier of yours.

343
00:19:47,905 --> 00:19:48,575
乌瑞纳斯？
 vorenus?  Was that it?

344
00:19:48,635 --> 00:19:50,276
是他吗？
Not the sullen Catonian one, I don't like him.

345
00:19:50,376 --> 00:19:51,706
不是那个一脸严肃的，

346
00:19:51,736 --> 00:19:52,736
我不喜欢他
 The cheerful brutish one.  Pullo.

347
00:19:53,076 --> 00:19:54,827
是那个长得像野兽的

348
00:19:55,237 --> 00:19:57,027
波罗，不错，就是他，
That's it. What extraordinary names these plebs have.

349
00:19:57,137 --> 00:20:00,138
他们的名字真够怪的

350
00:20:00,138 --> 00:20:01,438
波罗
Pullo.

351
00:20:02,038 --> 00:20:03,089
防守！
Defend! Shield.

352
00:20:04,149 --> 00:20:05,909
盾牌，盾牌
Shield.

353
00:20:06,510 --> 00:20:08,510
别乱挥
Don't wave it about.

354
00:20:10,740 --> 00:20:12,641
盾牌
Shield.

355
00:20:13,211 --> 00:20:14,961
够了！！
Enough!

356
