我没有搏击的天分
I have no soldiery stuff in me.

359
00:20:36,026 --> 00:20:38,157
这么强行去打只会让我发烧
And this exertion brings on a fever.

360
00:20:38,207 --> 00:20:39,517
我的脾脏都有感觉了
 I feel it in my spleen.  You're just not used to it.

361
00:20:39,527 --> 00:20:40,897
你只是没习惯罢了
It takes time. I've seen you kill.

362
00:20:40,907 --> 00:20:42,258
这是需要时间的，

363
00:20:42,288 --> 00:20:43,818
我见过你杀人
 There's plenty of soldier in you.  It's not the killing.

364
00:20:44,158 --> 00:20:46,429
你可是很有天分的

365
00:20:46,459 --> 00:20:47,429
不是杀人的问题，
It's the waving about of swords I find tedious.

366
00:20:47,459 --> 00:20:50,009
我只是觉得舞剑很没意思

367
00:20:50,029 --> 00:20:51,930
