374
00:21:02,762 --> 00:21:05,343
与其当庸手还不如什么都不会好
Best to be no swordsman at all than a middling swordsman.

375
00:21:08,163 --> 00:21:09,714
不准那样
Don't do that.

376
00:21:10,964 --> 00:21:11,954
