Excuse me.

377
00:21:19,206 --> 00:21:20,456
小主人
Young Dominus...

378
00:21:20,606 --> 00:21:22,057
我要请教一下你的意见
I need your advice on a delicate matter,

379
00:21:22,177 --> 00:21:24,727
 关于一件复杂的事情，如果你乐意的话，  没问题
 if you'd be willing?  I am.

380
00:21:25,537 --> 00:21:28,218
假设你看到了一件事情，让你怀疑另一件事情…
Suppose you saw something which made you suspect something--

381
00:21:28,308 --> 00:21:29,258
一件可怕的事情
something terrible.

382
00:21:30,639 --> 00:21:32,909
你会告诉被怀疑那个人的丈夫吗？
Would you tell the husband of the suspicious article?

383
00:21:32,909 --> 00:21:34,629
怀疑她什么？
Suppose suspicion of what?

384
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:38,770
另一个男人
 Another man.  Ah.

385
00:21:40,211 --> 00:21:42,531
我猜你说的是乌瑞纳斯和他的妻子
We are speaking of vorenus and his wife, I presume.

386
00:21:42,541 --> 00:21:43,531
我没有那么说过
I never said that.

387
00:21:46,452 --> 00:21:49,743
在我看来光是怀疑还是不够的
It seems to me that suspicion alone is not enough to speak.

388
00:21:50,083 --> 00:21:53,064
一旦怀疑到这种事情
Once spoken out, the suspicion of such depravity

389
00:21:53,064 --> 00:21:54,834
找到实在的证据才是正确的
is real enough to do the work of truth.

390
00:21:55,754 --> 00:21:57,435
要是你弄错了呢？
And what if you are mistaken?

391
00:21:57,925 --> 00:21:59,905
那么乌瑞纳斯就会因为你的错误蒙羞
Then vorenus is dishonored by error.

392
00:22:00,955 --> 00:22:04,106
