Facts are necessary. Without facts, you must remain silent.

393
00:22:06,087 --> 00:22:08,137
我知道你会说的那么透彻的
I knew you'd hit the jugular.

394
00:22:31,402 --> 00:22:34,053
拒绝休战
Refuses truce.

395
00:22:34,363 --> 00:22:36,253
现在怎么办？
What now?

396
00:22:37,514 --> 00:22:38,934
怎么办？
What now?

397
00:22:42,575 --> 00:22:44,235
多开心啊，嗯？
How happy, eh?

398
00:22:45,165 --> 00:22:46,466
身为奴隶
To be a slave.

399
00:22:47,866 --> 00:22:49,136
没有自己的意志
To have no will.

400
00:22:49,576 --> 00:22:51,097
不用做任何决定
To make no decisions.

401
00:22:51,537 --> 00:22:53,177
像段漂流的朽木
Driftwood.

402
00:22:53,777 --> 00:22:56,328
那会是多么宁静的事啊
How very restful it must be.

403
00:23:08,881 --> 00:23:12,502
 伊拉斯提斯·富罗门  百夫长
 Erastes Fulmen.  Centurion.

404
00:23:15,412 --> 00:23:16,893
我来是想问一下你的建议
I have come to seek your counsel.

405
00:23:17,193 --> 00:23:18,743
非常乐意
Always happy to help a friend.

406
00:23:19,783 --> 00:23:21,654
我想问你借点钱
I need to borrow some money

407
00:23:21,654 --> 00:23:23,704
听人说你有朋友从事贷款这个行业
and I am told you have friends in the lending trade.

408
00:23:24,224 --> 00:23:26,175
不错
I do.

409
