还不起钱就得受罪的
Man can't pay, he may have to suffer.

422
00:23:56,362 --> 00:23:59,212
我要是把你介绍给放贷的
Was I to introduce you to a lender,

423
00:23:59,212 --> 00:24:02,093
就像是把两头狼放到一个笼子里
I would be putting two wolves into one cage.

424
00:24:02,133 --> 00:24:03,773
没有一方会得到好处
To neither's benefit.

425
00:24:05,204 --> 00:24:05,924
不错，
You're right. You're right.

426
