像我这样的人？ 铁汉
 A man like me.  A hard man.

431
00:24:18,077 --> 00:24:21,637
恺撒第13军团的百夫长
First Spear Centurion in Caesar's mighty 13th.

432
00:24:21,677 --> 00:24:23,538
 我已经退役了  没关系
 I'm no longer in the army.  No matter.

433
00:24:23,638 --> 00:24:25,028
就你的样子已经足够了
Your bearing is enough.

434
00:24:26,508 --> 00:24:30,339
你可以把你的荣耀和力量借给做生意的人
You would lend dignity and strength to business transactions.

435
00:24:30,349 --> 00:24:32,500
如果你愿意的话，我就想雇用你
If you like, I could use you myself.

436
00:24:32,610 --> 00:24:34,450
让你看看那些羡慕的眼光
Show you the onions.

437
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:36,611
谢谢你的好意，不过
That's good of you,

438
00:24:36,911 --> 00:24:39,291
我还不清楚你要我作甚么？
but I still don't see what I would do exactly.

439
00:24:41,182 --> 00:24:45,173
你来和我一起解决一些麻烦
You would come with me to discourage trouble.

440
00:24:45,183 --> 00:24:48,503
没有人会跟百夫长找麻烦的
No one's going to mess with a First Spear Centurion.

441
00:24:48,613 --> 00:24:50,544
做保镖？
I'd be a bodyguard.

442
00:24:56,455 --> 00:24:58,145
会有很多钱
Good money.

443
00:25:00,426 --> 00:25:02,066
我告诉过你的，我告诉过你的！
I told you! I told you!

444
00:25:02,226 --> 00:25:04,757
对不起，我情不自禁，我没法…
I'm sorry, I couldn't help it. I can't--

445
00:25:04,957 --> 00:25:06,047
去你的，
Damn you! Damn her! I am your wife.

446
00:25:06,057 --> 00:25:07,428
我可是你的妻子！
Me. I am your wife.

447
00:25:07,458 --> 00:25:09,388
我，你的妻子

448
00:25:10,428 --> 00:25:11,509
莱蒂！
Lyde!

449
00:25:32,503 --> 00:25:34,014
真好看
That's lovely.

450
00:25:35,064 --> 00:25:36,964
看起来不像军人吧？
It's not too army-like?

451
00:25:37,004 --> 00:25:39,055
像个做生意的
Like a man of deep business.

452
00:25:39,055 --> 00:25:41,575
我不是生意人，只是个保镖
I'm no business man. I'm just a bodyguard.

453
00:25:42,436 --> 00:25:43,446
刚开始嘛
It's a start.

454
00:25:58,779 --> 00:25:59,839
赛维莉亚是恺撒的情妇
Please please, just for me.

455
00:26:16,503 --> 00:26:18,624
大家都怎么了？
What is the matter with everybody?

456
00:26:23,145 --> 00:26:24,165
恺撒的御用吹萧
Lock him up, girls! Lock him up!

457
00:26:26,384 --> 00:26:28,375
Ohh! Oy, Calpurnia!

458
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:29,978
Ooh, yes!

459
00:26:35,047 --> 00:26:37,318
