460
00:26:40,169 --> 00:26:42,599
 卡普尼娅…  不要管那些风言风语
 Calpurnia-  Do not trouble yourself with denial.

461
00:26:42,639 --> 00:26:45,460
 我不是故意的  离开她，我不会再说了
 I did not intend to.  Be rid of her and we'll say no more.

462
00:26:45,460 --> 00:26:48,701
 我们别…  否则就离婚
 Let us not-  Or divorce will follow.

463
00:26:49,381 --> 00:26:52,041
或许那不足以阻拦你
Perhaps that is not enough to deter you.

464
00:26:52,081 --> 00:26:55,062
那就那样吧，反正我是不会关心的
Be that as it may, I am indifferent.

465
00:26:57,813 --> 00:26:59,633
