I know it.

468
00:27:04,184 --> 00:27:05,284
恺撒狂操赛维莉亚
Bring me out the smaller scales.

469
00:27:06,324 --> 00:27:09,875
 百夫长，你来的正好  公民
 Centurion, you're right on time.  Citizen.

470
00:27:11,606 --> 00:27:13,146
我们为什么不在市场上见面？
Why do we not meet in the Forum?

471
00:27:13,186 --> 00:27:16,957
市场只是给那些快完成的交易，是公开的
Forum's only for closing deals, putting a hand on it public-like.

472
00:27:23,858 --> 00:27:26,509
别吹了！
Enough of that Teuton droning!

473
00:27:26,549 --> 00:27:28,880
要是你真想学那些无业游民那样吹口哨
If you want to whistle like someone's bum boy,

474
00:27:28,947 --> 00:27:30,938
吹点好听的罗马小调
whistle a good Roman song at least.

475
00:27:34,551 --> 00:27:36,411
她老是抱怨我像头大象
And she complained I was like an elephant.

476
00:27:36,411 --> 00:27:38,142
塔基特，我的小鸭子
Tanjit, my honey duck,

477
00:27:38,342 --> 00:27:40,802
 你看起来很好嘛  伊拉特斯·富罗门
 you're looking well.  Erastes Fulmen.

478
00:27:40,842 --> 00:27:43,173
向你妈妈问好
I kiss your mother's feet.

479
00:27:43,213 --> 00:27:45,153
