Would you like something to eat, drink?

481
00:27:47,764 --> 00:27:52,065
 来点葡萄酒吧  我们没有酒，牛奶如何？
 Wine will do.  We do not have wine. Milk, perhaps?

482
00:27:52,065 --> 00:27:54,625
