Humor. very good.

484
00:27:59,096 --> 00:28:01,627
非得要我到这里来我觉得很不高兴，塔基特
I'm sad to have to come here, Tanjit.

485
00:28:01,657 --> 00:28:03,557
非常不高兴
I'm very depressed.

486
00:28:03,607 --> 00:28:05,598
我原以为我们都是生意人
I thought we were businessmen.

487
00:28:05,688 --> 00:28:08,118
