00:29:35,838 --> 00:29:37,459
去死吧
Kiss my ass.

510
00:29:38,589 --> 00:29:40,609
割了他的喉咙
Cut his throat.

511
00:29:46,751 --> 00:29:48,241
快割！
Cut it!

512
00:30:11,396 --> 00:30:13,667
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

513
00:30:28,900 --> 00:30:30,791
