You refused him?

517
00:30:41,863 --> 00:30:44,224
我还能怎么样？
What else was I to do?

518
00:30:44,264 --> 00:30:46,404
 我又不是强盗  你当然不是了
 I am no bandit.  Of course you're not.

519
00:30:46,434 --> 00:30:48,045
你不能像从前那样杀人了
You couldn't do other than you did.

520
00:30:48,105 --> 00:30:50,545
不过我们怎么给租金啊？
But how are we to pay the rent?

521
00:30:51,025 --> 00:30:54,186
怎么养活孩子们？
How are we to feed the children?

522
00:31:02,638 --> 00:31:04,108
他来了！
He's here!

523
