我真高兴！我还以为你不会…
I'm so glad! I thought you might not--

524
00:31:08,999 --> 00:31:11,420
抱歉我不能呆下去了
I regret I cannot stay.

525
00:31:12,610 --> 00:31:15,441
我是来道别的
I've come to say goodbye.

526
00:31:16,031 --> 00:31:17,111
道别？
Goodbye?

527
00:31:17,171 --> 00:31:20,342
我要南下追击庞贝
I'm going south in pursuit of Pompey,

528
00:31:20,362 --> 00:31:23,723
我们不会再见面了
and we shall not see each other again.

529
00:31:24,733 --> 00:31:26,403
 什么？永不？ 永不
 What, never?  Never.

530
00:31:29,154 --> 00:31:30,804
别这么开玩笑
Don't joke so.

531
00:31:30,834 --> 00:31:33,125
