How can you say that?

535
00:31:54,330 --> 00:31:56,850
 我们彼此爱着对方
We love each other.

536
00:31:57,140 --> 00:31:57,912
 是的
Be assured,

537
00:31:57,982 --> 00:32:00,273
并不是我不爱你
it is not that l do not love you.

538
00:32:00,301 --> 00:32:02,451
